      <title>世界银行称未来两年巴基斯坦经济增速预计低于 3%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/pakistan-growth-seen-below-3-for-next-2-years-world-bank-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据世界银行的最新预测，巴基斯坦本财年经济增长预计将有所回升，但未来两年仍将保持在3%以下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/pakistan-growth-seen-below-3-for-next-2-years-world-bank-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 07:40:38 GMT</pubDate>
